Nice direction—Taflo AI as an enterprise AI company feels serious, trusted, and scalable.

Here’s a clean, Silicon‑Valley‑style Enterprise AI homepage you can use right away.

`html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Taflo AI — Enterprise Intelligence</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #111827;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    / Header /
    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      background: #ffffff;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2563eb;
    }
    nav a {
      margin-left: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #374151;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    / Hero /
    .hero {
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f3f6ff, #ffffff);
    }
    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 2.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
      color: #4b5563;
    }
    .hero .cta {
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      padding: 0.8rem 1.6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: none;
      background: #2563eb;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      padding: 0.8rem 1.4rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #374151;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-left: 0.75rem;
    }

    / Sections /
    .section {
      max-width: 1040px;
      margin: 3.5rem auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }
    .section h3 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .section p {
      color: #4b5563;
      max-width: 720px;
    }

    / Grid /
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.8rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 1.6rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      transition: 0.2s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      border-color: #2563eb;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }
    .card h4 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    / Footer /
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Taflo AI</h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="#platform">Platform</a>
      <a href="#use-cases">Use Cases</a>
      <a href="#security">Security</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h2>Enterprise AI That Scales With Your Business</h2>
    <p>
      Taflo AI helps enterprises automate decisions, streamline operations, and unlock insight from data —
      with a platform that is secure, compliant, and built for real‑world scale.
    </p>
    <div class="cta">
      <button class="btn-primary">Request a Demo</button>
      <button class="btn-secondary">Talk to Sales</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="platform">
    <h3>The Taflo AI Platform</h3>
    <p>
      A unified enterprise AI layer that connects to your existing systems, learns from your data,
      and delivers intelligent workflows across the organisation.
    </p>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h4>End‑to‑End Automation</h4>
        <p>From data ingestion to decision execution, Taflo AI automates complex business processes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Flexible Integration</h4>
        <p>Connect to CRMs, ERPs, data warehouses, and internal tools with modern APIs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Human in the Loop</h4>
        <p>Review, approve, and refine AI decisions with clear controls and audit trails.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="use-cases">
    <h3>Enterprise Use Cases</h3>
    <p>
      Taflo AI is designed for teams that need reliable, explainable intelligence across critical functions.
    </p>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Operations</h4>
        <p>Automate ticket routing, approvals, and workflows to reduce manual work and response times.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Risk & Compliance</h4>
        <p>Detect anomalies, flag high‑risk activity, and support compliance reviews with AI‑driven insights.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Customer Experience</h4>
        <p>Power intelligent support, personalised responses, and self‑service experiences at scale.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="security">
    <h3>Security & Trust</h3>
    <p>
      Enterprise‑grade security is built into Taflo AI from day one — so you can deploy AI with confidence.
    </p>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Data Privacy</h4>
        <p>Your data stays under your control, with strict access policies and isolation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Governance</h4>
        <p>Role‑based access, logging, and policy controls for regulated environments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Reliability</h4>
        <p>Built for high availability and performance across mission‑critical workloads.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="contact">
    <h3>Contact the Taflo AI Team</h3>
    <p>Email: enterprise@taflo.ai</p>
    <p>LinkedIn: Taflo AI</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2026 Taflo AI — Enterprise Intelligence, Delivered
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
`

